products.title: Azurite Chenille Coral Pink Roman Blind
products.description: Their azurite chenille range consists of textured plains with a velour soft-feel finish. This soft coral pink roman blind fuses a plush, luxuy feel in a contemporary pink tone to create a on trend room feature that is bound to be noticed. At swift direct blinds, quality is important to us, which is why this roman comes with their free five year guarantee and customer-first service. Available as a matching curtain.
